verbose_text: On one hand visfatin exerts an insulin like effect, enhancing phosphorylation of IRS-1 and expression of PPARgamma [XREF_BIBR], but on the other hand it potentiates expression of some adhesion molecules, IL-6 and TNF-alpha [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
